desc: Triple c poultry is a wholesale online kebab, fresh chicken and meat supplier in Brisbane. We supply to all major restaurants, caterers and household buyers. We deliver to all areas of Brisbane and Gold coast. Our speciality products are chicken kebabs, fresh chicken meats, beef burger patties and frozen products.

layout.text: We Deliver or Orders can be picked up from Triple C's Warehouse at 22 Dollis Street, Rocklea. Please contact us on 3277 9608 to organise a day and time to pick up your order.
Triple C Poultry is a Brisbane-based, wholesale food and meat manufacturing, and distribution company. We supply our products to restaurants, schools, catering companies and the general public.
